{"tid":530811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"感謝黨！西北風吹珠海污染物來港 臭氧濃度創18年新高","createTime":"2018-01-16T07:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T07:24:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de400071271ec717f3fb909771931ceed0c8f7e7","tid":530811,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180116/large/1516086451_2a8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180116%2Flarge%2F1516086451_2a8b.jpg&h=2e5fa45e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環保署公佈去年空氣質素，臭氧濃度是自1999年有紀錄以來最高，一般監測站每立方米達51微克，較前年大增31%，路邊監測站達23微克，亦較前年增加21%。環保署指，去年總日照時間較前年增加19%，氣象條件有利臭氧形成。<br />\n<br />\n署方又發現，當吹偏西北風時，珠海口積聚區域性臭氧帶到香港西面，可令臭氧濃度暴升至每立方米逾250微克。而吹偏東風時，臭氧水平隨即急降至不足100微克。換言之，內地污染物隨風吹至影響香港。署方指，為改善區域臭氧問題，粵港兩地減少氮氧化物(NOx)和揮發性有機化合物(VOC)排放。<br />\n<br />\n而臭氧水平上升，車輛排放的一氧化氮轉化為二氧化氮，令去年路邊二氧化氮濃度較前年增加5%。至於去年的一氧化碳、二氧化硫濃度，就有輕微下跌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180116/57714463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F57714463&d=X9IW%2BGPfmw1%2FZ%2F0ymGgNcMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ce1e06df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F57714463&h=fcdce5a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180116/57714463</a>"}]}